{"id": "1402972573997863072", "channel_id": "1402929570046283856", "type": 0, "author_id": "1365539464839036978", "author_name": "torph.", "author_bot": false, "content": "Aequor? Do Caecus, Ramona, Miryam, Goliath.\n\n\nKeep pulling on standard till you get Tulu and Murphy. Once you got both of them, replace Goliath and Ramona with them.\n\n\nOnce Goliath reach e3(3 star), you can slot him in whenever you meet enemies with high atk buff. He can steal them. But otherwise, Tulu and Murphy is good damage reduction and tentacle damage escalation.", "timestamp": "2025-08-07T11:12:07.611000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1402929570046283856", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Who should i invest in and what are good aquar teams?", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1402972940319854592", "channel_id": "1402929570046283856", "type": 0, "author_id": "1365539464839036978", "author_name": "torph.", "author_bot": false, "content": "After you reach Goliath e3, Caecus e3, Tulu e1, I recommend switching to other realm like Chaos till you get Karen e3, Nautila e3, and 24 e1.\n\nThen after that, feel free to switch back to Aequor or other realm you might like or enter the wheel jail.", "timestamp": "2025-08-07T11:13:34.949000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-07T11:48:23.373000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1402929570046283856", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Who should i invest in and what are good aquar teams?", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545", "1400747088995811358"]}
